Improve rd-mode.el

- Avoid resetting rd-mode-map every time rd-mode is turned on, so that

commit.message:
Include MethodList in imenu
Closes #14

I used `(setq imenu-generic-expression '((nil "^[=+-]+.+" 0)))` with old rd-mode.el.
But it does not work with current rd-mode.el.
I want to support MethodList in imenu. (Headline of `+`, `++` are unused by <https://github.com/rurema/doctree>).

Include MethodList in imenu
Closes #14

I used `(setq imenu-generic-expression '((nil "^[=+-]+.+" 0)))` with old rd-mode.el.
But it does not work with current rd-mode.el.
I want to support MethodList in imenu. (Headline of `+`, `++` are unused by <https://github.com/rurema/doctree>).

Fix incompatibility between Ruby1.8 and Ruby1.9.

Kernel.#readlines makes ARGV empty. So,

Ruby1.8: ARGF.filename returns the filename even if ARGV is empty.
Ruby1.9: ARGF.filename returns "-" if ARGV is empty.
